[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なんか騒がしいわね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00446",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そ、そりゃあんだけ暴れりゃ野次馬も湧くって。\nとりあえずジェロンをおぶってこの場を――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00447",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボス、通報があったのはこの辺りです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00448",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "一人で突っ込まずに応援を要請したのは\nいい判断だ、タイニー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00449",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あ、ありがとうございます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00450",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "げっ……監察官殿……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00451",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "アルビーナ？　いったいどういうことだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00452",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ええと、これは色々込み入った事情がありまして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00453",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "その事情をすべて話してもらおう。\nブラオールの秩序のためにな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00454",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "で、でも、エルスさんたちを巻き込んでしまうかも\nしれないので……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00455",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "所轄で騒動になっている時点で、\nすでに巻き込まれているのだ。遠慮なく話せ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00456",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ちょっと、九偉人のことはあんまり世間に\n広めないほうがいいと思うんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00457",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "同感だけど、エルスさんの剣幕がすごくて……\nつい、私がやりましたって言っちゃいそう……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00458",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "一部始終、しっかり見てたよ。\nこの仮面の奥の、２つの眼でね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00459",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "変てこ仮面さん！　目撃者なんですか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00460",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ。この人たちの知り合いらしい三人組が\n派手に暴れたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00461",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そこで伸びてる獣人は、反撃しようとして返り討ちを\nくらったって寸法だよ。三人はすでに逃げちゃったね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00462",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ふむ……ということはアルビーナたちは\nあくまでも攻撃された被害者ということだな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00463",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "さあね。この場ではそうかもしれないが、\n因縁があるみたいだから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00464",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "先にどこか別の場所でこいつらが仕掛けて、\n今回お礼参りをされたって可能性もある",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そ、そんな……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "彼女たちからは、危険な匂いがする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00465",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "エルスさん、その、説明は難しいんすけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00466",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ああ。分かっているのは、今この場においては\nお前たちが被害者であるという点だけだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00467",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "むしろ到着が遅れて申し訳ない。\n同盟の秩序を維持するのが監察官の使命だというのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00468",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、謝らないでください！　こちらこそ、\n入国早々、街の人に迷惑をかけてしまって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00469",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……少なくとも、今後１週間は平和よ、多分。\nそれまでにはなんとかして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00470",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "二度とみんなが傷つかないよう、\nあいつらと話を付けるわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00471",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]